com.agorapulse.micronaut.grails

Class MicronautBeanImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.agorapulse.micronaut.grails.MicronautBeanImporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GrailsMicronautBeanProcessor.Builder

    public class MicronautBeanImporter
extends Object
    Defineds which Micronaut beans should be added into a Grails' Spring application context. The processor will then find all of the Micronaut beans of the specified types and add them as beans to the Spring application context.

    It can also manage beans to
